title: Blood On The Moon ( Western 1948) Robert Mitchum, Robert Preston & Barbara Bel Geddes

sources.title: Blood On The Moon Western 1948 Robert Mitchum Robert Preston Barbara Bel Geddes
sources.description: "Blood on the Moon" is a 1948 film noir Western directed by Robert Wise, featuring Robert Mitchum and Barbara Bel Geddes, centered around a cattle dispute and moral dilemmas
